       01  IN157-STR-EXPTED-RECORD.                                             
           05  IN157-STORE-NBR             PIC X(05)       VALUE SPACES.        
           05  IN157-STORE-NBR-9  REDEFINES                                     
               IN157-STORE-NBR             PIC 9(05).                           
           05  IN157-DEPT                  PIC X(04)       VALUE SPACES.        
           05  IN157-DEPT-9 REDEFINES IN157-DEPT                                
                                           PIC 9(04).                           
           05  IN157-CLASS                 PIC X(04)       VALUE SPACES.        
           05  IN157-CLASS-9 REDEFINES IN157-CLASS                              
                                           PIC 9(04).                           
           05  IN157-SKU                   PIC X(08)       VALUE SPACES.        
           05  IN157-SKU-9 REDEFINES IN157-SKU                                  
                                           PIC 9(08).                           
      *                                                                         
      *  HAD TO DEFINE INTR-UPC-ID AS 10 DIGITS AND REDEFINES AS SHOWN          
      *  BECAUSE S9(9) CAN ACTUALLY HOLD 10 DIGITS UP TO A CERTAIN              
      *  POINT.  MOVING THE FIELD FROM DB2 DCLGEN TO A S9(9) WILL               
      *  TRUNCATE THE LEFT MOST DIGIT, SO DEFINING AS BELOW WILL                
      *  PREVENT TRUNCATION.                                                    
           05  IN157-INTR-UPC-ID           PIC S9(10) COMP VALUE ZEROES.        
           05  FILLER REDEFINES IN157-INTR-UPC-ID.                              
               10  FILLER                  PIC X(04).                           
               10  IN157-INTR-UPC-ID-4     PIC X(04).                           
               10  IN157-INTR-UPC-ID-SPC REDEFINES IN157-INTR-UPC-ID-4          
                                           PIC S9(9)  COMP.                     
      *                                                                         
           05  IN157-ADJ-DATE              PIC X(10)       VALUE SPACES.        
           05  IN157-BAL-QTY               PIC S9(9)       VALUE ZEROES         
                                                     COMP.                      
           05  IN157-ADJ-QTY REDEFINES IN157-BAL-QTY                            
                                           PIC S9(9) COMP.                      
           05  IN157-RTL-AMT               PIC S9(7)V9(2)  VALUE ZEROES         
                                                     COMP-3.                    
           05  IN157-EXTD-RTL-AMT          PIC S9(13)V9(2) VALUE ZEROES         
                                                     COMP-3.                    
           05  IN157-ENT-ID                PIC S9(9) COMP  VALUE ZEROES.        
           05  IN157-FSCL-MN-END-DTE       PIC X(10)       VALUE SPACES.        
           05  IN157-FSCL-MN-NBR           PIC X(02)       VALUE SPACES.        
           05  IN157-PO-NBR                PIC S9(9) COMP  VALUE ZEROES.        
           05  IN157-RCVR-SEQ-NBR          PIC S9(9) COMP  VALUE ZEROES.        
           05  IN157-OUTBOUND-TRAILER-ID.                                       
               10  IN157-OTBND-TRIP-ID     PIC S9(9) COMP  VALUE ZEROES.        
               10  IN157-OTBND-TRIP-MORE   PIC X(01)       VALUE SPACES.        
                   88  IN157-MULTI-OTBND-TRIP              VALUE '*'.           
                   88  IN157-SINGLE-OTBND-TRIP             VALUE SPACES.        
